cu.explanation_en: Setting the local SCTP data port to an invalid number (99999) will cause socket binding failures and prevent F1 data plane establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting the gNB name to an empty string will cause identification and logging issues in the DU configuration.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB 名稱設定為空字串會在 DU 配置中造成識別和記錄問題。
